data.description: Welcome to 626 Tarpualin! This charming 3/2 located in the Newport subdivision is loaded with upgrades which include a custom gas fireplace, granite countertops, crown moulding, high ceilings, a jetted garden tub, and more! Don't forget the breakfast bar, large fully fenced back yard with gate, all stainless appliances, and walk-in closet. This home quells your fears with a new A/C unit (2022), new water heater (2021), new carpet and flooring (2021), and a new dishwasher (2022)! Schedule your private showing today!
